data_for_corr <- heptathlon_data[, 1:7]
PerformanceAnalytics::chart.Correlation(data_for_corr, histogram = TRUE, pch = 19)

pca_results <- PCA(heptathlon_data, 
                   quanti.sup = 8,  
                   graph = FALSE) 

print(pca_results)
